This paper deals with deep learning for camera pose regression, which is a topic that falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). The paper also discusses novel loss functions and optimal weighting, which are topics related to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper leverages geometry to improve performance, which is a topic related to graphics (cs.GR).
